{"word":"G2579 - κἄν - kán - kan - And if","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κἄν</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">kán</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kan</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">And if</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>NA / Not Available</span>"},{"paragraph":"உம், இருந்தாலும், ஆகிலும் - எச்சம்"},{"paragraph":"1. and if"},{"paragraph":"2. also or even if"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2532 - καί - kaí - kahee/2532\">G2532</a> nad <a href=\"#/G1437 - ἐάν - eán - eh-an'/1437\">G1437</a>; <i>and</i> (or <i>even</i>) <i>if:</i> - and (also) if (so much as), if but, at the least, though, yet.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}